{
  "bookId": "laozi-heshanggong-wiki",
  "num": 65,
  "title": "第六十五章（淳德）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "古之善為道者，非以明民，將以愚之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "民之難治，以其智多。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故以智治國，國之賊；"
    },
    {
      "text": "不以智治國，國之福。"
    },
    {
      "text": "知此兩者亦楷式。"
    },
    {
      "text": "常知楷式，是謂玄德。"
    },
    {
      "text": "玄德深矣，遠矣，"
    },
    {
      "text": "與物反矣！"
    },
    {
      "text": "然後乃至於大順。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "說古之善以道治身及治國者，不以道教民明智巧詐也，將以道德教民，使質樸不詐偽。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "民之所以難治者，以其智多而為巧偽。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "使智慧之人治國之政事，必遠道德，妄作威福，為國之賊也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不使智慧之人治國之政事，則民守正直，不為邪飾，上下相親，君臣同力，故為國之福也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "兩者謂智與不智也。常能智者為賊，不智者為福，是治身治國之法式也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "玄，天也。能知治身及治國之法式，是謂與天同德也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "玄德之人深不可測，遠不可及也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "玄德之人與萬物反異，萬物欲益己，玄德施與人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "玄德與萬物反異，故能至大順。順天理也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
